      <b>Disclaimer:</b> All product and company names are trademarks™ or registered® trademarks of their respective holders. Use of them does not imply any affiliation with or endorsement by them.
      <br>
      <center>Made with <div class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart"></div> by <a href="http://www.ksaurabh.net">Kumar</a>!</center>
    </div>
</div>
</div>
<br>
<br>
<%= render 'layouts/footer' %>
</body>
</html>
